utilities

Class SLL

  • java.lang.Object
    • utilities.SLL
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, List

    public class SLL
extends java.lang.Object
implements List, java.io.Serializable
    Single Linked List Class. Implements custom "List" interface and serializable. This uses the class "SLLNode" to store elements in a list of connected objects. Each object (except the last) has a reference to the next node in the list. Thoroughly tested with 100% coverage in SLLTest.
    Version:
    2, April 9th, 2017
    Author:
    729380
    See Also:
